   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n498_slave_david-3-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n498_slave_david-3-c" mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>Well, it should have been told yesterday. You're already late.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer David$<BR>If someone who is polluted by Dragon's blood like you touches the Dragon's Jewel, it will be absorbed into that someone's body.<BR>If the person doesn't have the power for it, he can be turned into a <FONT color=#a82424>monster</FONT>. By the way ... why are you crying?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
